<item>
            <title>[LU-13518] Lustre 2.12.4 on Centos 7.8 ? When does 2.12.5 come out ?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13518</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;br/&gt;
I have to simple questions:&lt;br/&gt;
1) Will lustre 2.12.4 client/server run on Centos 7.8 just fine ?  I didn&apos;t see it as a support version in the documentation.&lt;br/&gt;
2) When do you think lustre 2.12.5 will come out ?&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks,&lt;br/&gt;
Mike&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Centos 7.7 and 7.8 on various hardware.</environment>
        <key id="59049">LU-13518</key>
